<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>プレオープン限定 モニター様募集 | 出張もみほぐし</title>
<meta name="description" content="プレオープン限定モニター募集。通常料金のほぼ半額で出張もみほぐしをご体験いただけます。上富田町・田辺市・白浜町対応。">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy-900: #0d1b2a;
    --navy-800: #14253a;
    --navy-700: #1b2f4d;
    --navy-600: #243a5e;
    --gold: #c9a961;
    --line-green: #06C755;
    --line-green-hover: #05b04c;
    --bg-cream: #f7f5f0;
    --text-dark: #1a2638;
    --text-light: #ffffff;
    --text-muted: #6b7280;
    --border-light: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  body {
    font-family: "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", "Hiragino Sans", "Yu Gothic", "Meiryo", sans-serif;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    background: var(--bg-cream);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 16px;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--bg-cream);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ===== Section 1: First View ===== */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-900) 0%, var(--navy-700) 100%);
    color: var(--text-light);
    padding: 56px 28px 64px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -30%;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy-900);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-title .accent {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 32px;
    display: block;
    margin: 8px 0;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 14px;
    opacity: 0.85;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-divider {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin: 32px auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-message {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-detail {
    font-size: 15px;
    opacity: 0.9;
    line-height: 1.9;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ===== Section Common ===== */
  section {
    padding: 64px 28px;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy-900);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .section-title::after {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    width: 32px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin: 16px auto 0;
  }

  /* ===== Section 2: Empathy ===== */
  .empathy {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .worry-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .worry-list li {
    padding: 18px 24px;
    background: var(--bg-cream);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--navy-900);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .empathy-message {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e0d5;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e0d5;
  }

  /* ===== Section 3: Service ===== */
  .service {
    background: var(--bg-cream);
  }

  .service-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(13, 27, 42, 0.06);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .service-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .service-card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .service-card .highlight {
    color: var(--navy-700);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ===== Section 4: Monitor ===== */
  .monitor {
    background: var(--navy-900);
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .monitor .section-title {
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .monitor-intro {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .benefit-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, #b89345 100%);
    color: var(--navy-900);
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.25);
  }

  .benefit-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .benefit-main {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .benefit-price {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .monitor-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  /* ===== Section 5: Schedule ===== */
  .schedule {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .schedule-card {
    background: var(--bg-cream);
    border: 1px solid #e5e0d5;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .schedule-card.featured {
    background: var(--navy-900);
    color: var(--text-light);
    border-color: var(--navy-900);
  }

  .schedule-date {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy-900);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .schedule-card.featured .schedule-date {
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .schedule-time {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .schedule-card.featured .schedule-time {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .schedule-status {
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .schedule-status.urgent {
    background: #d63838;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .schedule-status.available {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy-900);
  }

  .schedule-warning {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #d63838;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ===== Section 6: CTA ===== */
  .cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-800) 0%, var(--navy-600) 100%);
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta .section-title {
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .cta-intro {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .step-list {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .step-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 20px 20px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .step-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy-900);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .step-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .line-button {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--line-green);
    color: #ffffff;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 22px 20px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.35);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .line-button:hover,
  .line-button:active {
    background: var(--line-green-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.45);
  }

  .line-icon {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-right: 8px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    color: var(--line-green);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding: 16px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 4px;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  /* ===== Section 7: Notes ===== */
  .notes {
    background: var(--bg-cream);
    padding: 48px 28px;
  }

  .notes-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .notes-list {
    list-style: none;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 8px 24px;
  }

  .notes-list li {
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ebe0;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 18px;
  }

  .notes-list li::before {
    content: "・";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .notes-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  /* ===== Footer ===== */
  footer {
    background: var(--navy-900);
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    font-size: 12px;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* ===== Sticky LINE Button (mobile) ===== */
  .sticky-cta {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 16px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: calc(100% - 32px);
    max-width: 448px;
    z-index: 100;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .sticky-cta.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  .sticky-cta a {
    display: block;
    background: var(--line-green);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 16px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.4);
  }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (min-width: 481px) {
    body {
      padding: 0;
      background: #1a1a1a;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 380px) {
    .hero-title { font-size: 22px; }
    .hero-title .accent { font-size: 28px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 20px; }
    section { padding: 56px 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <!-- ① ファーストビュー -->
  <section class="hero">
    <span class="hero-badge">PRE-OPEN LIMITED</span>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      プレオープン限定<br>
      <span class="accent">モニター様募集</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      通常料金の<strong>"ほぼ半額"</strong>で<br>
      出張もみほぐしをご体験いただけます
    </p>
    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
    <p class="hero-message">「その疲れ、<br>今日のうちに整えませんか？」</p>
    <p class="hero-detail">
      ご自宅でそのまま施術<br>
      そのまま休めます
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- ② 共感 -->
  <section class="empathy">
    <span class="section-label">YOUR WORRIES</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">こんなお悩み<br>ありませんか？</h2>
    <ul class="worry-list">
      <li>肩や腰が重い</li>
      <li>疲れが抜けない</li>
      <li>外に出るのがしんどい</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="empathy-message">
      そんな方に向けた<br>
      <strong>出張リラクゼーション</strong>です
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- ③ サービス説明 -->
  <section class="service">
    <span class="section-label">OUR SERVICE</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">サービスについて</h2>
    <div class="service-card">
      <p>
        ご自宅へお伺いし、<br>
        <span class="highlight">お一人おひとりの状態</span>に合わせて<br>
        施術いたします
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <p>
        <span class="highlight">移動の負担がなく</span>、<br>
        施術後はそのまま<br>
        ゆっくりお休みいただけます
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ④ モニター募集 -->
  <section class="monitor">
    <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--gold);">MONITOR CAMPAIGN</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">モニター募集中</h2>
    <p class="monitor-intro">
      現在プレオープン期間のため<br>
      モニター様を募集しております
    </p>
    <div class="benefit-box">
      <div class="benefit-label">特典</div>
      <div class="benefit-main">施術料金</div>
      <div class="benefit-price">ほぼ半額</div>
    </div>
    <p class="monitor-note">※ 簡単なアンケートにご協力をお願いいたします</p>
  </section>

  <!-- ⑤ 日程 -->
  <section class="schedule">
    <span class="section-label">SCHEDULE</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">ご予約可能日程</h2>

    <div class="schedule-card featured">
      <div>
        <div class="schedule-date">5月12日</div>
        <div class="schedule-time">20:00 〜 23:00</div>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-status urgent">残り1枠</div>
    </div>

    <div class="schedule-card">
      <div>
        <div class="schedule-date">5月19日</div>
        <div class="schedule-time">特別枠にてご案内</div>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-status available">受付中</div>
    </div>

    <div class="schedule-card">
      <div>
        <div class="schedule-date">5月26日</div>
        <div class="schedule-time">特別枠にてご案内</div>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-status available">受付中</div>
    </div>

    <p class="schedule-warning">※ 埋まり次第終了</p>
  </section>

  <!-- ⑥ 予約方法（CTA） -->
  <section class="cta" id="cta">
    <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--gold);">EASY RESERVATION</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">ご予約はとても簡単</h2>
    <p class="cta-intro">3ステップで完了します</p>

    <div class="step-list">
      <div class="step-item">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-text">
          下記ボタンから<br>
          <strong>公式LINE</strong>を友だち追加
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-item">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-text">
          トーク画面で<br>
          <strong>「モニター」</strong>と送信
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step-item">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-text">
          自動で予約フォームが届きます<br>
          → <strong>日時を選択して完了</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="https://lin.ee/pCsJffH" class="line-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <span class="line-icon">L</span>LINEで予約する
    </a>

    <a href="https://lin.ee/pCsJffH" class="line-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="background: #ffffff; color: var(--line-green); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border: 2px solid #ffffff;">
      今すぐ空き枠を確認
    </a>

    <div class="cta-secondary">
      「まだ空いてますか？」<br>
      だけでも大丈夫です
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ⑦ 注意事項 -->
  <section class="notes">
    <div class="notes-title">― 注意事項 ―</div>
    <ul class="notes-list">
      <li>対応エリア：上富田町・田辺市・白浜町</li>
      <li>遠方は事前決済のみ</li>
      <li>男性専門（女性はご夫婦・同伴のみ対応）</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <footer>
    出張もみほぐし<br>
    プレオープン記念モニター募集
  </footer>

</div>

<!-- Sticky CTA -->
<div class="sticky-cta" id="stickyCta">
  <a href="https://lin.ee/pCsJffH" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <span class="line-icon">L</span>LINEで予約する
  </a>
</div>

<script>
  // Show sticky CTA after scrolling past hero
  const stickyCta = document.getElementById('stickyCta');
  const hero = document.querySelector('.hero');

  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    const heroBottom = hero.offsetTop + hero.offsetHeight;
    if (window.scrollY > heroBottom) {
      stickyCta.classList.add('visible');
    } else {
      stickyCta.classList.remove('visible');
    }
  });
</script>

</body>
</html>
